Module it.polimi.ingsw.triton.launcher
Package it.polimi.ingsw.triton.launcher.client.model

Class ClientModel

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.triton.launcher.utils.obs.Observable<Object>
it.polimi.ingsw.triton.launcher.client.model.ClientModel
public class ClientModel extends Observable<Object>
This class saves the state of the game and relevant information. It's updated every time the server model sends messages with updated objects. This class contains all the objects useful for the player and these are used for visualization in cli/gui view.
